prompts.frontCover: Vibrant and humorous watercolor painting for a greeting card front. A woman is lounging blissfully on a giant, cartoonishly oversized boba tea cup that has washed ashore on a cute, tropical beach. The boba cup is translucent, showing oversized tapioca pearls inside, and has a giant, colorful straw sticking out. She is dressed in a casual summer outfit, holding a smaller, normal-sized boba tea, smiling as she takes a sip. The beach scene is idyllic, with soft white sand, gentle turquoise waves, and a couple of cartoon palm trees. In the sand, there are little hand-drawn sandcastles shaped like boba cups. The entire scene is rendered in a bright, cheerful watercolor style with soft, blended colors and playful, loose linework. Centered in the sky above the scene, the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" is written in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script. 2D flat illustration, charming cartoon style.
